button_group.set_pressed_button(button_group.get_button_list()[index]) sometimes not works properly.

It happens because in cpp file buttons store in Set, and get_button_list() not uses sort!!!
but get_pressed_button_index()  uses sort: blist.sort_customNode::Comparator();

after similar list sort_custom in gdscript (using Node.is_greater_than) button_group works OK.
Need add sorting in cpp file in method :
void ButtonGroup::get_button_list(List<BaseButton*> *p_buttons) const {

```
for(Set<BaseButton*>::Element *E=buttons.front();E;E=E->next()) {

    p_buttons->push_back(E->get());
}
